==歐洲==
[[File:Konsumverbot.svg|thumb]]
 
大多數[[歐洲|歐洲]]國家都把18歲定為購買酒類的最低年齡。但[[奧地利|奧地利]]、[[比利時|比利時]]、[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[直布羅陀|直布羅陀]]、[[列支敦士登|列支敦士登]]、[[盧森堡|盧森堡]]、[[馬耳他|馬耳他]]、[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]、和[[瑞士|瑞士]]（[[提契諾州|提契諾州]]除外）把最低購買年齡維持在不滿18歲的年齡，允許未成年人完全或有限地獲得酒精。[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]在2005年、<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rp-online.de/politik/deutschland/eu-will-alkoholkauf-erst-ab-18-erlauben-aid-1.1607191 |title=EU will Alkoholkauf erst ab 18 erlauben |author=AFP, dpa |date=2005-02-26 |language=de |website=rp-online.de |access-date=2018-03-23 |archive-date=2018-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323220150/http://www.rp-online.de/politik/deutschland/eu-will-alkoholkauf-erst-ab-18-erlauben-aid-1.1607191 }}</ref>2007年、<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.abendblatt.de/politik/europa/article107217172/Die-EU-will-Alkohol-erst-ab-18-Jahren-freigeben.html |title=Die EU will Alkohol erst ab 18 Jahren freigeben |author=AFP, dpa |date=2007-03-13 |language=de |website=abendblatt.de |access-date=2018-03-23 |archive-date=2021-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118091842/https://www.abendblatt.de/politik/europa/article107217172/Die-EU-will-Alkohol-erst-ab-18-Jahren-freigeben.html }}</ref>和2015年<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.welt.de/politik/ausland/article140181484/EU-Parlament-will-Alkohol-unter-18-verbieten.html |title=EU-Parlament will Alkohol unter 18 verbieten |author=Christoph B. Schiltz |date=2015-04-27 |language=de |website=welt.de/politik |access-date=2018-03-23 |archive-date=2022-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415102053/https://www.welt.de/politik/ausland/article140181484/EU-Parlament-will-Alkohol-unter-18-verbieten.html }}</ref>在歐盟層面曾為最低購買年齡為18歲進行協調，但未達成協議。
 
飲酒/購買年齡，或限制未成年人取得酒精的法律變化的時間表如下：
 
*2002年，西班牙自治區[[馬德里|馬德里]]、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elinconformistadigital.com/modules.php?op=modload&name=News&file=article&sid=56 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20150408124810/http://www.elinconformistadigital.com/modules.php?op=modload&name=News&file=article&sid=56 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2015-04-08 |title=La ley seca aprobada en Madrid |author=Marlowe |date=2002-03-07 |language=es |website=elinconformistadigital.com |access-date=2015-04-07 }}</ref>[[瓦倫西亞|瓦倫西亞]]、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.joves.net/estas-d-acord/augmentar-l-edat-per-a-consumir-alcohol |title=El Conseller Blasco propone aumentar la edad legal para el consumo de alcohol |date=2002 |language=es |website=joves.net |access-date=2015-04-07 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414042742/http://www.joves.net/estas-d-acord/augmentar-l-edat-per-a-consumir-alcohol |archive-date=2015-04-14 }}</ref>和[[加泰隆尼亞|加泰隆尼亞]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lasdrogas.info/noticias/453/cataluna-eleva-hasta-los-18-anos-la-edad-minima-para-poder-comprar-alcohol.html |title=Cataluña eleva hasta los 18 años la edad mínima para poder comprar alcohol |date=2002-02-28 |language=es |website=lasdrogas.info |access-date=2015-04-07 |archive-date=2018-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180324103147/http://www.lasdrogas.info/noticias/453/cataluna-eleva-hasta-los-18-anos-la-edad-minima-para-poder-comprar-alcohol.html }}</ref>將其最低購買年齡提高為18歲。在此之前，瓦倫西亞和馬德里的最低購買年齡為16歲，而在加泰隆尼亞，16歲或17歲的未成年人可在店內和店外購買[[酒精濃度|酒精濃度]]（ABV）達到23%的酒類。
